---
title: Grilled Salmon and Shrimp Boil with Garlic-Lemon Butter and Green Salad
description: Flavours of a classic Southern shrimp boil are fitted to the grill for this flavour-packed summer dinner. The final drizzle of a lemon-infused garlic butter puts it over the top!
